snippet.title: Apex Legends: Wild Iron Event Trailer
snippet.description:
The Wild Iron Event settles an ancient rivalry—cybernetic supremacy versus the raw power of nature. 

Wildcard gets explosive with a new Mythic Flatline and new Wild Card abilities to help you make things go boom. Mad Maggie and Seer updates blow up the scene, plus an opportunity to get new Legendary Skins and the new Fuse-inspired Mythic Flatline.

Learn more: http://x.ea.com/apxl/wild-iron-event

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play* battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC via EA App, Epic Games Store and Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.
